---
title: Winter-Warming Sea Bass with Tapas-Style Potatoes and Charred Peppers
description: During the festive season, fish is often a welcome respite and this recipe is exactly that. Sea bass is beautiful paired with light and zesty flavours like lemon and fresh parsley. Chef Mimi has incorporated some classic Spanish flavours with the patatas bravas for a Christmas dish with a twist!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/lemony-sea-bass-6500e31b-f342b5f0.jpg
